{"about_the_game":"<strong>Whiskey &amp; Lemons</strong> introduces a new Career mode, that adds role playing elements to the Grand Tactician: The Civil War campaigns. Create your own character, follow your commanders' orders, gain prestige and promotions. When in position to do so, play a key role in your nation's war-effort. This is your Civil War story!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138830/extras/RolePlay.png?t=1705830647\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138830/extras/line.png?t=1705830647\" /><br><strong>Features:</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138830/extras/bullet.png?t=1705830647\" /><strong>Your Story:</strong> Create your own commander character with unique personality and skills. Role-play through the war to see your character develop.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138830/extras/bullet.png?t=1705830647\" /><strong>Do Your Part:</strong> Start your career as a low ranking commander, following orders from your higher-ups. Gain promotions to allow more control over the course of the war.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138830/extras/bullet.png?t=1705830647\" /><strong>Manage Your Career:</strong> Gain prestige and earn money to equip yourself and your unit, recruit staff officers to your headquarters and decide your personal actions.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138830/extras/bullet.png?t=1705830647\" /><strong>Make History:</strong> Play a key role in your nation's war-effort, and become one of the legendary Civil War generals. Read about your epic adventures in your Biography.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138830/extras/bullet.png?t=1705830647\" /><strong>Regimental Level Campaign:</strong> A new campaign covering the Eastern Theater of the Civil War, that can be played in normal and career modes. Offers regimental level game play.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138830/extras/bullet.png?t=1705830647\" /><strong>New Features:</strong> Deployable garrisons, and Grouper command level for Army Groups in main campaigns and Armies in regiment level campaigns.","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2138830?t=1705830647","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2138830?t=1705830647","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138830/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1705830647","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138830/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1705830647","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Downloadable Content","id":21},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<strong>Whiskey &amp; Lemons</strong> introduces a new Career mode, that adds role playing elements to the Grand Tactician: The Civil War campaigns. Create your own character, follow your commanders' orders, gain prestige and promotions. When in position to do so, play a key role in your nation's war-effort. This is your Civil War story!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138830/extras/RolePlay.png?t=1705830647\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138830/extras/line.png?t=1705830647\" /><br><strong>Features:</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps